title: Gomez, Underwood to perform at American Music Awards
text: American Music Awards Nominations! 00:37 The American Music Awards nominations are in! Pop princess Taylor Swift leads with a total of 6 noms while Ed Sheeran and The Weeknd grabbed five each! Stars like Sam Hunt, Jason Aldean, Wiz Khalifa, and Fetty Wap also grabbed noms. And there are 10 nominations for the coveted Artist of the Year... You Might Like
